--- Consequence -> { name_key, action_key } for localized rendering.
--- name_key:   short caption (e.g. "Alpha Kill Targeted").                   For config / debug context.
--- action_key: full phrase that names the consequence as an ongoing action.  For PDA marker, warfare tooltip, news.
---             e.g. "Chasing Alpha Killer", "Investigating a Massacre Site".
--- Both resolved via game.translate_string at render time.
